<s> I'm more interested in solving that problem, and that is what Crit accomplishes, because it seems to me that we achieve a very interesting multiplying power of knowledge that way -- a new kind of network effect made possible by backward links, akin to the kind of augmentation that happened when the Web gave us forward links.  </s>
